  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Development of the Care Strategy with Emphasis on Empathic Communication Based on the Non-Violent Communication Methodology</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project contributes to the qualification and strengthening of the accompaniment processes for the victims of forced disappearance within the framework of fulfilling the objective of the Unit for the Search for Forced Disappearance (UBPD) in Colombia. This is accomplished through a strategy of training and multiplication of tools to avoid emotional wear and tear and to disseminate the humanitarian values that guide the UBPD mandate among its partners. This is supported by the non-violent communication methodology.</narrative>
  </description>
